HEADWORD: jacklight
<hw>jacklight</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>A portable source of light, as an
oil lantern or electric light, used as a lure for hunting at
night.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> jack.</syn>⟦br⟧
